You can interact with the table

You can use regex to search this table!

For example, either in the search bar (searches entire table) or in specific column filter (searches specific column), type:

  • seed|insect to keep rows that mentions either seed OR insect.
  • ^(?=.*seed)(?=.*invert).* mentions seed AND insect
